<main>
  <section>
    <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:#666;margin-bottom:.5rem;">
      <em>By <strong>Rocco DeLuca</strong>, Licensed Insurance Agent &bull; Published 2026-04-04 &bull; Last updated 2026-04-04</em>
    </p>
    <h1 style="text-align:center;">Your 2026 Medicare Checklist — Vernal &amp; Uintah Basin</h1>
    
        <p>Whether you are new to Medicare or reviewing your current plan, this checklist covers everything Uintah Basin residents should evaluate before making a decision for 2026.</p>

        <h2>Before You Compare Plans</h2>
        <p><strong>Gather your information:</strong> List of current doctors and specialists with addresses. List of all prescription medications with dosages and frequency. Preferred pharmacy name and location. Current Medicare card (Original Medicare, Advantage, or both). Any upcoming scheduled procedures or specialist referrals. Income information if you may qualify for Extra Help or Medicaid.</p>

        <h2>Questions to Answer</h2>
        <p><strong>Coverage needs:</strong> Are your current doctors accepting your plan next year? Has your plan's formulary changed for any of your medications? Has your plan's premium, copay, or deductible changed? Do you need dental, vision, or hearing coverage? Do you travel or spend time outside Utah? Have you had any major health changes this year?</p>

        <h2>Key 2026 Numbers to Know</h2>
        <p>Part B premium: {usd(f.partB.premium, { cents: true })}/month. Part B deductible: {usd(f.partB.deductible)}/year. Part A hospital deductible: {usd(f.partA.deductible)}. Part D annual out-of-pocket cap: $2,000. Insulin cap: $35/month. Annual Enrollment Period: October 15 – December 7.</p>

        <h2>Action Steps</h2>
        <p>Review your Annual Notice of Change (ANOC) letter from your current plan. Compare plans using our <a href="free-medicare-comparison-vernal.html">free comparison tool</a>. Call <a href="tel:+14352195120">435-219-5120</a> for a personalized review. Enroll in the best plan before December 7. Set a calendar reminder to review again next year.</p>

        <h2>Get Help With Your Checklist</h2>
        <p>Bring this checklist to your appointment with Rocco at Smith's Pharmacy, or go through it over the phone. We will work through every item and ensure you have the best coverage for 2026.</p>

        <p>Related: <a href="medicare-open-enrollment-2026.html">Open Enrollment 2026</a> | <a href="when-to-enroll-medicare-utah.html">Enrollment deadlines</a> | <a href="medicare-cost-uintah-county.html">Cost breakdown</a></p>
        <p><em>Source: <a href="https://www.medicare.gov" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Medicare.gov</a>.</em></p>
        
